    {
      "start": 522.68,
      "end": 523.04,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 523.32,
      "end": 529.4,
      "text": "이 배우에 대한 background knowledge를 알고 나니까 좀 더 소린이 달리 보이기 시작할 것 같네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 530.3,
      "end": 531.72,
      "text": "오늘 장면 먼저 듣고 올까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 532.32,
      "end": 536.26,
      "text": "When I was young, I passionately wanted two things."
    },
    {
      "start": 536.88,
      "end": 538.02,
      "text": "I wanted to get married."
    },
    {
      "start": 538.44,
      "end": 539.58,
      "text": "I wanted to become an author."
    },
    {
      "start": 540.28,
      "end": 541.58,
      "text": "I never managed either one."
    },
    {
      "start": 542.16,
      "end": 545.75,
      "text": "Even the thought of her makes my heart race."
    },
    {
      "start": 546.09,
      "end": 547.75,
      "text": "I am insanely happy."
    },
    {
      "start": 548.01,
      "end": 551.88,
      "text": "The Constantine's 외삼촌, 소린."
    },
    {
